<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Aplikasi Kelulusan SMAN 2 MOJOKERTO 2026</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="app">
        <!-- SLIDE 1: LOGIN -->
        <section id="login-slide" class="slide active">
            <div class="background-overlay"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="login-card">
                    <div class="school-logo-container">
                        <img src="sman2_mojokerto_logo_1778130553024.png" alt="Logo SMAN 2" class="school-logo">
                    </div>
                    <h1>Sistem Informasi Kelulusan</h1>
                    <p class="subtitle">SMAN 2 MOJOKERTO</p>
                    
                    <form id="login-form">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <label for="username">Username</label>
                            <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Masukkan Username" required autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <label for="password">Password</label>
                            <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Masukkan Password" required autocomplete="off">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-login">Masuk</button>
                    </form>
                    <p id="error-msg" class="error-msg">Username atau Password salah!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SLIDE 2: RESULT -->
        <section id="result-slide" class="slide">
            <div class="background-overlay"></div>
            <nav class="top-nav">
                <div class="user-info">
                    <span id="display-user" class="user-name">Hai MOCHAMAD DIN PANULUH</span>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-links">
                    <a href="#" id="logout-btn">Logout</a>
                </div>
            </nav>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="result-container">
                    <div class="app-header">
                        <p>Aplikasi Kelulusan SMAN 2 MOJOKERTO 2026</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="result-card">
                        <h2 class="student-name" id="student-name-display">MOCHAMAD DIN PANULUH</h2>
                        
                        <div class="status-badge">
                            <div class="badge-icon">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="status-text">Maaf, Anda Tidak Lulus</h3>
                        </div>

                        <div class="message-box">
                            <p>Bagi yg tidak lulus, tetap semangat! Teruslah belajar dan jangan menyerah. Kesuksesan menanti di depan.</p>
                            <p class="secondary-msg">Mohon maaf coba lagi</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="visitor-counter">
                            <p>Anda pengunjung ke :</p>
                            <div class="counter-box">
                                <span class="counter-label">Visitor Counter</span>
                                <span class="counter-value">3413</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
